OBJECTIVE:
Provide REST API endpoints for asset registration, token creation, minting, and trading.

ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA:
✅ POST /api/v11/tokenization/rwa/register - Register RWA asset
✅ POST /api/v11/tokenization/token/create - Create token
✅ GET /api/v11/tokenization/token/{id} - Get token info
✅ POST /api/v11/tokenization/token/{id}/mint - Mint tokens
✅ GET /api/v11/tokenization/registry - List all tokens

API SPECIFICATIONS:

1. Register Asset
POST /api/v11/tokenization/rwa/register
Body: {
  assetType: REAL_ESTATE | EQUITY | BOND | COMMODITY | ARTWORK
  name, description, totalValue, jurisdiction
  metadata: { address, sqft, yearBuilt }
  fractional: { enabled, totalShares, minInvestment }
  documents: [ { type: TITLE_DEED, fileId } ]
}
Response: { assetId, status: PENDING_VERIFICATION }

2. Create Token
POST /api/v11/tokenization/token/create
Body: {
  assetId, name, symbol
  type: FUNGIBLE | NFT | SEMI_FUNGIBLE
  totalSupply, decimals, pricePerToken
  kycRequired: true, amlRequired: true
  dividendsEnabled: true, annualYield: 9.0
}
Response: { tokenId, smartContractAddress }

3. Mint Tokens
POST /api/v11/tokenization/token/{id}/mint
Body: {
  recipient: 0x...
  amount: 1000
}
Response: { txHash, newTotalSupply }

4. List Tokens
GET /api/v11/tokenization/registry?assetType=REAL_ESTATE
Response: {
  tokens: [
    { tokenId, name, symbol, type, supply, price }
  ],
  totalCount: 150
}

EFFORT: 2 days
PRIORITY: High
